 during the initial negative breakdown, namely as a result of strong\ncurrents flowing in the final stage of successive IBPs, extending backward\nthrough both the IBP itself and the negative streamer breakdown preceding the\nIBP.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Sep 2020 22:24:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2020 20:28:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
