ons: Through this novel machine learning-based method we have\nshown accurate and reproducible generation of beam data for linac commissioning\nfor routine radiation therapy. This method has the potential to simplify the\nlinac commissioning procedure, save time and manpower while increasing the\naccuracy of the commissioning process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Sep 2020 03:06:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Oct 2020 07:54:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-07"}
