encies present in complex systems, this lookahead variation\nis a useful extension to the toolkit of data scientists, in particular for\nfinancial machine learning, where conditions (a) and (b) are typically met.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Sep 2020 11:31:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Oct 2020 01:54:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2020 14:11:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 04:21:00 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 31 Mar 2021 14:24:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-01"}
