ance of considering the worst-case\nscenarios in investigating the most effective methods of epidemic containment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Sep 2020 22:43:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 Nov 2020 05:53:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-17"}
